<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Support - Time with Kids</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007AFF;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .support-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #007AFF;
        }
        .contact-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007AFF, #0056CC);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .contact-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,122,255,0.3);
        }
        .faq-item {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007AFF;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .faq-item h3 {
            color: #007AFF;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #007AFF;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .back-btn:hover {
            background: #0056CC;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007AFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
    <script src="language-switcher.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Time with Kids Support</h1>
            <p>We're here to help you make the most of your time with your children</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="support-section">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>For questions or bug reports, please contact us through the following methods:</p>
            <a href="https://forms.google.com/your-support-form" class="contact-btn">Contact Form</a>
            <p>Or email: support@santamaruapp.com</p>
        </div>

        <div class="support-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Q: How do I use the app?</h3>
                <p>A: After launching the app, register your child's information from the [Settings] menu. Then, on the main screen, you can start recording time spent with your child by selecting activities and categories.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Q: My data disappeared</h3>
                <p>A: Please use the backup feature. Go to [Settings] → [Data Management] to create a backup. If you've already backed up, you can restore your data from there.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Q: Tell me about in-app purchases</h3>
                <p>A: Basic features are free to use. Premium features include advanced analytics, unlimited goal setting, and cloud backup. You can upgrade anytime from the settings.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Q: How do I set goals?</h3>
                <p>A: Go to [Goals] from the main menu, tap the "+" button, and set your desired time goals for different activities with your child.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Q: Can I use the app on multiple devices?</h3>
                <p>A: Yes, if you have a premium subscription, you can sync your data across multiple devices using iCloud backup.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-section">
            <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>App won't launch:</strong> Try restarting your device and ensure you have the latest version of iOS</li>
                <li><strong>App is running slowly:</strong> Try clearing the app cache from Settings → Data Management → Clear Cache</li>
                <li><strong>Notifications not working:</strong> Check your device's notification settings and ensure the app has permission to send notifications</li>
                <li><strong>Data sync issues:</strong> Make sure you're signed in to iCloud and have a stable internet connection</li>
                <li><strong>App crashes:</strong> Try force-closing the app and reopening it. If the problem persists, restart your device</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="support-section">
            <h2>App Information</h2>
            <p><strong>Current Version:</strong> 1.0.0</p>
            <p><strong>Minimum iOS Version:</strong> iOS 14.0 or later</p>
            <p><strong>App Size:</strong> Approximately 25MB</p>
            <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 19, 2024</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <a href="index-en.html" class="back-btn">← Back to Home</a>
            <p>
                <a href="index-en.html">Home</a> | 
                <a href="support-en.html">Support</a> | 
                <a href="privacy-policy-en.html">Privacy Policy</a>
            </p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 santamaruapp. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
